  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My friends and I had decided-- practiced-- that we could lay under the wagon, under the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was plenty of room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Let the train go over us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then, at this particular spot-- which is a spot which we had practiced and seen in our mind a thousand times-- you know, like you look at the same picture.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You know exactly where it is, and what you have to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You have to run like the wind down the slopes and disappear in the woods, where then, the underground is, will tell you where to go, what to do, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It's only on this spot, where the train goes very, very slow-- like when steep uphill.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That's where you go under the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now, where I was sitting, like I'm sitting here, on this one wall, there was this much of a board, which my friends saw we had, the last week was smuggled in, of course, all sorts of, you know, saw and hammer and things like this.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And it was interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Nobody cared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Boden didn't care, the kommandant didn't care, because he knew there would be jumpers.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
